  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (COMPOUND-03 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package declares assuranceLevel Medium and an Accepted decision outcome; however, multiple credibility factors have achievedLevel strictly below requiredLevel, constituting a Critical W-AR-02 weakener that is inconsistent with the stated assurance and acceptance. The inconsistency is the embedded COMPOUND-03 signal.",
