      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must have documented V&V test suite with regression coverage for hemolysis-relevant flow regimes; configuration management must be version-controlled with audit trail.",
      "rationale": "Solver version control and regression suite exist but coverage of non-Newtonian and high-shear hemolysis regimes is incomplete. SQA documentation does not include formal sign-off for MRL 5 deployment. Achieved level 3 falls short of required level 4."
