      "rationale": "Grid convergence study performed on three meshes; GCI for hemolysis index ranges from 8–14% across operating points, exceeding the 5% threshold. Achieved level 3 is substantially below required level 5, representing the primary Critical gap (W-AR-02 trigger)."
