      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions (inlet velocity profiles, fluid rheology, temperature) must match simulation inputs within stated uncertainty bounds for all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "Inlet velocity profiles are matched at mean values; turbulence intensity at the inlet was not measured experimentally and is assumed from literature. Fluid temperature during hemolysis testing was not recorded continuously. Achieved level 3 falls below required level 4."
    },
    {
