      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model and hemolysis power-law model must be justified with sensitivity analysis; alternative model forms must be compared and the selected form defended for the COU flow regime.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected without comparison to LES or RSM for the high-shear rotating geometry. Hemolysis power-law constants (C, alpha, beta) are taken from Giersiepen et al. without assessment of applicability to continuous-flow VAD conditions. Achieved level 2 is far below required level 5."
