    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team concludes that the CFD hemolysis prediction model achieves Medium assurance and is accepted for regulatory submission. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is in place and the primary hemolysis QoI is directly mapped to the clinical decision variable. Remaining factor gaps are noted as areas for future improvement but are judged acceptable given the conservative clinical threshold margin observed in the output comparison.",
